closure_text:
May 30 Effective at 1:10PM, parking areas at Walden Pond State Reservation in Concord will be closed to ALL incoming visitors, until further notice, as the park has reached its maximum safe number of visitors. Continue to follow 
@waldenpondstate
 for parking status.

reopen_text:
Thursday June 4 - Effective at 2:53pm, parking areas at Walden Pond State Reservation have re-opened. Continue to follow 
@waldenpondstate

 for parking status.

Walden Pond State Reservation
@waldenpondstate
Saturday, June 6 - Effective at 12:12pm, parking areas at Walden Pond State Reservation have re-opened. Continue to follow for updates.

closure_text:
Walden Pond State Reservation
@waldenpondstate
Sunday July 5, 2020 at 2:55pm Walden Pond State Reservation has reached its maximum safe number of people in the park and is CLOSED to all incoming visitors. No dropping off passengers. No stopping along the road. Check for updates.

Walden Pond State Reservation
@waldenpondstate
Sunday 11\8\20 12:11pm has reached its maximum safe number of people in the park and is CLOSED to all incoming visitors until crowd thins. NO drop-offs. NO parking offsite.  NO stopping on rt. 126. Check back for updates.
